scene.message:
Nanjo: {ctl0f:1}, I may{nl}
have said this before, but{nl}
what about the hospital? We{nl}
aren't going?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Toro's got guts, man!{nl}
I mean, going after Ayase{wait_fr:32}{nl}
of all people... no thanks,{nl}
not me!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: I don't like seeing{nl}
someone who's serious get{nl}
laughed at.{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: I-I had this weird{nl}
dream! A girl was saying{nl}
"help me"...{waitkey}{clearbox}Think maybe it's a prophetic{nl}
dream? Maybe there's a girl{nl}
out there waiting for me{waitkey}{nl}
to save her? Th-{wait_fr:32}that'd be{nl}
so cool...{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Kenta Yokouchi, aka Toro.{nl}
Loves to eat. Strong as an{nl}
ox, but timid.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: I saw it! Toro{nl}
confessed to Ayase and got{nl}
flat-out turned down!{waitkey}And he still won't stop{nl}
pestering her!{waitkey}{ret}
